I. Preliminaries

Loading libraries

library("tidyverse")
library("tibble")
library("msigdbr")
library("ggplot2")
library("dplyr")
library("grex")
library("org.Hs.eg.db")
library("AnnotationDbi")
library("clusterProfiler")

II. Gene Ontology Enrichment Analysis

Load the list of differentially expressed genes.

deg <- read.delim("../data/patient/differentially-expressed-genes-untargeted.csv", sep=",")
rownames(deg) <- deg$X
deg$X <- NULL
deg

Perform pathway enrichment analysis.

genes <- rownames(deg)
enriched <- enrichGO(
  gene = genes,
  OrgDb = org.Hs.eg.db,
  ont = "CC",
  pAdjustMethod = "BH",
  keyType = "ENSEMBL",
  pvalueCutoff = 0.05,
  readable = TRUE
)

as.data.frame(enriched)
plot(barplot(enriched, showCategory = 20))

genes <- rownames(deg)
enriched <- enrichGO(
  gene = genes,
  OrgDb = org.Hs.eg.db,
  ont = "BP",
  pAdjustMethod = "BH",
  keyType = "ENSEMBL",
  pvalueCutoff = 0.05,
  readable = TRUE
)

as.data.frame(enriched)

genes <- rownames(deg)
